review.description:
@eat24 @yelpnyc #foodporn I LOVE this place! It's has a small setting for those romantic nights and it also have a great atmosphere. If you desire to listen to soothing mellow tunes during your stay and eat tasty food; I would say do not hesitate to visit this establishment. Did I forget to mention the $1 mimosa's? Yup, it cost only $1 and it taste refreshing.

So what are my favorite dishes when I visit this Resturant? I have to say the Mac & Cheese and chicken & waffles. I know there are probably many other selections to choose from the menu, but I wanted to try something recommended by my waiter. I am truly happy with his selection. Scanning around I have noticed there's a mini stage for performances. I had to confirm if this is true. The manager have explained and confirmed it's accurate. So I decided to re-visit and experience something different. I can say I had a wonderful time. My recommendation is to reach out to them and see what on their plate regarding special events. 

I would give the 5 stars by far. My ratings can change if experience a change in customer service.
